ENTRY            A1465   20260317   20260508   20260508       A133
SUBENT        A1465001   20260317   20260508   20260508       A133
BIB                 13         25
TITLE      Study of the reaction 7Li(p,alpha)alpha up to 12 MeV
           proton energy
AUTHOR     (G.S.Mani,R.Freeman,F.Picard,A.Sadeghi,D.Redon)
REFERENCE  (J,NP,60,588,1964)
FACILITY   (VDGT,2FR SAC)
INSTITUTE  (2UK MAN,2FR SAC)
SAMPLE     The targets of 7Li were prepared by vacuum evaporation
           99.9% enriched 7Li metal on to 500 ug/cm2 thick
           nickel backing. The lithium deposit was around
           30 ug/cm2 and it was allowed to remain in the
           atmosphere for sufficient time after evaporation to
           form the stable hydroxide.
DETECTOR   (SOLST) Three solid-state detectors mounted on a
           rotatable top lid.
METHOD     (BCINT)
MONITOR    (3-LI-7(P,A)2-HE-4,,SIG)
MONIT-REF  (A1475005,Cassagnou+,J,NP,33,449,1962)
REL-REF    (A,A1357001,Jeronimo+,J,NP,38,11,1962)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
HISTORY    (19801003C) Compilation Produced by RFNC-VNIIEF Sarov
           (19990321U)CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases.
           (20080826A) SD. Occasionally the entry was deleted in
            2001. Now it is restored.
           (20260317A) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           MONITOR added.
ENDBIB              25
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           28
